---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Aryan D Haritsa">

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04]">
      <svg width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <defs>
          <pattern id="cross-about" x="0" y="0" width="32" height="32" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <path d="M16 0v32M0 16h32" stroke="#1A365D" stroke-width="0.3"/>
          </pattern>
        </defs>
        <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#cross-about)"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-10 relative">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--color-faint)] font-medium mb-3">Background & Interests</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-accent);">
        About
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-6"><div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[var(--color-accent)]/20 to-transparent"></div></div>

  <!-- Bio -->
  <section class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em] font-bold text-[var(--color-accent)] border-b-2 border-[var(--color-accent)] pb-1.5 mb-8" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">Bio</h2>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-[var(--color-ink)] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I am a final-year B.Tech Computer Science student at PES University, Bengaluru, and a first-generation researcher. I am currently interning at Nagravision Kudelski, where I am building agentic AI systems that orchestrate across enterprise knowledge bases, data lakes, and communication platforms.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-[var(--color-accent-soft)]/50 rounded-lg p-5 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/10">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.06em] font-bold text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-3">Research Interests</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          My research interests center on understanding and building systems that exhibit general intelligence. Specifically, I work on <strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)] font-medium">mechanistic interpretability</strong> -- reverse-engineering what neural networks actually compute, understanding the algorithms learned during training rather than just input-output behavior. I am drawn to <strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)] font-medium">scaling laws</strong> and their implications for architecture design: how compute, data, and parameters trade off, and what this means for choosing between transformer, state-space, and recurrent architectures. I study <strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)] font-medium">transformer and diffusion model architectures</strong> in depth -- attention mechanisms, state-space models like Mamba, and the architectural inductive biases that shape what models can learn. I work with <strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)] font-medium">fine-tuning techniques</strong> including LoRA, QLoRA, and quantization methods (MXFP4, GPTQ, AWQ) to understand their effects on model behavior beyond just parameter efficiency. A central thread in my work is <strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)] font-medium">mesa-optimization</strong> -- investigating models that learn to optimize internally during forward passes, creating emergent optimization loops that are not explicitly trained for. Finally, I focus on <strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)] font-medium">mathematical reasoning in AI</strong>, pushing LLMs to solve competition-level mathematics through tool integration and structured reasoning.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>
        Where I am going: a research lab residency or MTech, then founding an AGI-focused company. Self-funded, deliberately. I believe the most meaningful work comes from taking the long path -- building deep technical foundations before trying to scale, and maintaining the independence to pursue questions that matter even when they are not fashionable.
      </p>

      <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)]">
        I am honest about being early. I do not yet have published papers or a PhD. What I do have is curiosity that does not quit, taste for the right problems, and a willingness to spend years on questions that matter. I would rather build real understanding slowly than collect credentials quickly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SVG Wave Divider -->
  <div class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-6 my-6"><div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[var(--color-accent)]/15 to-transparent"></div></div>

  <!-- Education -->
  <section class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-6 pb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em] font-bold text-[var(--color-accent)] border-b-2 border-[var(--color-accent)] pb-1.5 mb-8" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">Education</h2>

    <div class="space-y-5">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-md bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1A365D] to-[#2D5AA0] text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">PES</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">PES University, Bengaluru</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">B.Tech, Computer Science and Engineering</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-1">
            <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-faint)]">2022 -- 2026</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-faint)]">&middot;</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-[var(--color-accent)]">CGPA 8.05 / 10</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-md bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2D5AA0] to-[#4A90D9] text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">PU</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">Sadhana PU College</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">Pre-University (12th)</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-1">
            <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-faint)]">PCMC</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-faint)]">&middot;</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-[var(--color-accent)]">94.4%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-md bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4A90D9] to-[#7AB8F5] text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">10</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">SRKVS</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">SSLC (10th)</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-1">
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-[var(--color-accent)]">99.4%</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-faint)]">&middot;</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">5th rank in state</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Experience -->
  <section class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-6 pb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em] font-bold text-[var(--color-accent)] border-b-2 border-[var(--color-accent)] pb-1.5 mb-8" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">Experience</h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="border border-[var(--color-rule)] rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#1A365D] to-[#4A90D9]"></div>
        <div class="p-5">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-1">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">Nagravision Kudelski</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">Intern -- Agentic AI Systems</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-faint)] whitespace-nowrap ml-4">Jan -- May 2026</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            Building Project Rick -- an agentic chatbot that orchestrates across AWS Bedrock, Knowledge Bases, S3, Athena, Glue, and MS Teams. Designing the agent architecture, tool routing, and retrieval pipelines for enterprise knowledge access.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-[var(--color-rule)] rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#2D5AA0] to-[#7AB8F5]"></div>
        <div class="p-5">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-1">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">August AI</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">Intern -- Machine Learning</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-faint)] whitespace-nowrap ml-4">Jun -- Aug 2025</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            Worked on ML systems for Tata 1mg (grace platform) and Manipal Group. Applied machine learning to healthcare and enterprise use cases.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SVG Wave Divider -->
  <div class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-6 my-6"><div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[var(--color-accent)]/15 to-transparent"></div></div>

  <!-- Competitions -->
  <section class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-6 pb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em] font-bold text-[var(--color-accent)] border-b-2 border-[var(--color-accent)] pb-1.5 mb-8" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">Competitions</h2>

    <div class="grid gap-4">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent-soft)]/30 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/10">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">AI</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">
            AIMO Prize 3
            <span class="text-xs font-normal text-[var(--color-accent)] ml-2">36/50</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-0.5">Solo entry. 3 weeks of work. Kaggle competition for AI mathematical olympiad solving.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent-soft)]/30 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/10">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">HV</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">
            Hackverse 2025, MIT Bangalore
            <span class="text-xs font-normal text-[var(--color-accent)] ml-2">7th Place</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-0.5">Built WaySafe -- a smart tourism safety application. September 2025.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent-soft)]/30 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/10">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">AR</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">
            ARC AGI 3
            <span class="inline-flex items-center text-xs px-2 py-0.5 bg-green-50 text-green-700 border border-green-200 rounded-full font-medium ml-2">Active</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-0.5">Currently competing on Kaggle. Abstract reasoning and generalization benchmark.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em] font-bold text-[var(--color-accent)] border-b-2 border-[var(--color-accent)] pb-1.5 mb-8" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">Contact</h2>

    <div class="bg-[var(--color-accent-soft)]/50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/10">
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        Interested in collaborating on research, discussing AI systems, or just want to say hello? I am always happy to connect.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm">
        <a href="mailto:aryanharitsa@gmail.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white rounded-md hover:bg-[var(--color-accent)]/90 transition-colors font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          aryanharitsa@gmail.com
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/Aryanharitsa" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 border border-[var(--color-rule)] text-[var(--color-muted)] rounded-md hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
          GitHub
        </a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/aryan-haritsa-60292925b" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 border border-[var(--color-rule)] text-[var(--color-muted)] rounded-md hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
          LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
